1-6 Enrolment details
For the purposes of the definition of enrolment details in section 5 of the Act,
enrolment details in relation to a person are the information mentioned in
sections 3-2, 3-3 and 3-4 in relation to the person (as an applicant).

Note: Item 54 of table 1 in section 6 of the Act covers a holder of an Australian financial
services licence who arranges for a person to receive a designated service.
