3-8 Request to remove entry from Reporting Entities Roll-required
information
For the purposes of paragraph 51G(2)(b) of the Act, a request by a person under
subsection 51G(1) of the Act to remove the person's name and enrolment details
from the Reporting Entities Roll must contain the following information:
